body_html:
Just hit the same problem. Here is the issue:
I followed the installation instructions from Sherry Moore's tf-tutorial github page. Her instructions rely on using --upgrade $TF_BINARY_URL when using pip to install tensor flow, and she provides the old 0.2.0 URL.
I uninstalled tensorflow, and reinstalled it using: pip install tensorflow, and it grabbed version 1.0.1 automatically... after that, no more problems importing this model_fn
